casebody.data:
Wednesday, December 15, 1993

MOTION DOCKET

93-2137. Harris v. Babcock & Wilcox Co.

Summit County, No. 16017. On motion for stay. Motion denied.

Wright, Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.

On motions to dismiss appeal, to strike opposition to stay, and to dismiss cross-appeal and motion to strike. Motions denied.
